{"tid":1503742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"824 核彈集中討論區","createTime":"2019-08-25T05:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T05:53:10.000Z","uid":23991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"241c2d410ab46d0797a338229d6402a9981986e3","tid":1503742,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"首先 825葵荃青 需要你<br />\n[推上熱門]8.25 荃葵青大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502896</a><br />\n<br />\n整合：<br />\n內地監控燈柱後台有香港資料<br />\n【終極大核彈！！！】【斷正】監控燈柱操作界面　中共監視香港大計　香港即將玩完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501789</a><br />\n<br />\n驚賊實彈用空尖彈 一中即死<br />\n哇, 屌你老母, 差佬D 子彈係達姆彈(空尖彈)黎, 打中人必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502125</a><br />\n<br />\n催淚彈過期日子被磨走同有手足check到現場山埃濃度超標<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/562250074239981/posts/729568000841520?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F562250074239981%2Fposts%2F729568000841520%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRULnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=c18d0793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/562250074239981/posts/729568000841520?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵懷疑製造假禁制令及封站運狗<br />\n[超突發] 狗鐵個閪 court 印已變回 High Court ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501041</a><br />\n<br />\n麗晶花園改密碼 唔比黑衫住戶入 再報警告手足非法集結<br />\n[有樓戰線] 麗晶花園件事就係班中產唔理政治既後果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503513</a><br />\n<br />\n驚賊闖入德福花園開tg 傷及小朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/singmajority/photos/a.355959845080077/384801672195894?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsingmajority%2Fphotos%2Fa.355959845080077%2F384801672195894%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRULnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=3ca1d39c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/singmajority/photos/a.355959845080077/384801672195894?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n水平瞄頭 差啲又多一隻眼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/501070300016124/posts/2514927708630363?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F501070300016124%2Fposts%2F2514927708630363%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRULnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=d7f7fa8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/501070300016124/posts/2514927708630363?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\ncctvb又幫黑警洗白<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/439167530273435?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2Fphotos%2Fa.417570699099785%2F439167530273435%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRULnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=92d44b74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/439167530273435?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 仲有好多單 多到有啲麻目<br />\n但呢啲仆街<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一個都唔可以放過</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23826991d5a3ad0d6cfe7e0e74475d8942671a80","tid":1503742,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"自推十連1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a83b8ad92ed07cb25fee42c265e1273db05156","tid":1503742,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1701ed9d726aaa26496b1bb4cb72552ec7b60b","tid":1503742,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/face